<doc id="645629" wikidata="Q260667" url="?curid=645629" title="Länder">
<text>&#x27; (singular &#x27;) or &#x27; (singular &#x27;) is the name for (federal) states in two German-speaking countries. It may more specifically refer to:
* States of Austria, the nine federal subdivisions of Austria
* States of Germany, the 16 federal subdivisions of Germany

